Date: Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:13:48 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] CMake FMU export adding missing source files (#14368)

* Install minpackP.h to external_solver dir

  - Fixes failed copy of minpackP.h to source-code FMU

* Copying ModelicaExternalC from CMake

  - ModelicaExternalC C source files are now installed with
    ModelicaExternalC CMake file instead of C runtime makefile.
  - Changed install location to install/include/omc/ModelicaExternalC/
  - Updated copy call in SimCodeMain.mo to use new location

* Adding test for FMU export with MSL Table

  - Test FMU export
  - Test recompilation with FMPy
